From: Matthieu Baerts <matttbe@kernel.org>
Subject: [PATCH] DO-NOT-MERGE: mptcp: add CI support

Currently supported:

- Github Actions:
  - build-validation: check different combinations of validation
  - checkpatch: use checkpatch.pl to validate new commits
  - notif: send notifications to the IRC channel and emails
  - Update TopGit tree: sync with net and net-next and then override the
    export branches.

- Cirrus:
  - Run tests in a KVM: selftests, kunit, packetdrill, etc.

Signed-off-by: Matthieu Baerts <matttbe@kernel.org>
